data.description: This charming home has so much to offer! Beautiful original windows let in tons of light and  this home offers all the amenities of a modern home with an addition completed in 2010. Amenities include heated en-suite bathroom, mudroom, and garage floors and a dog washing station. The home has a new roof and furnace 2023. It is in need of paint and carpet but those finishing touches will make it yours. It is conveniently located near the new Lake Links trail with great walkability and offers association access to White Bear Lake!
